Race.SpecificTitle: PW Law Enforcement Dist. Prop. No. 1 of 2 -- 9.53 Mills Renewal - Sheriff - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Law Enforcement District Proposition No. 1 of 2
(Tax Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall the Law Enforcement District of the Parish of Assumption, State of Louisiana (the "District"), continue to levy a nine and fifty-three hundredths (9.53) mills tax on all the property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $1,908,200 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2024 and ending with the year 2033, for the purpose of providing additional funding for the District?

Race.SpecificTitle: PW Law Enforcement Dist. Prop. No. 2 of 2 -- 10 Mills Renewal - Sheriff - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Law Enforcement District Proposition No. 2 of 2
(Tax Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall the Law Enforcement District of the Parish of Assumption, State of Louisiana (the "District"), continue to levy a ten (10) mills tax on all the property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $2,002,300 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2024 and ending with the year 2033, for the purpose of providing financing to the Assumption Parish Sheriff's Office to enable it to continue to furnish services at the general level of services now being provided?
